Maintainer: Chuyao Xu  <cxu870@aucklanduni.ac.nz>
Description: Some response-adaptive randomisation methods commonly found in literature are included in this package.
             These methods include the randomized play-the-winner rule, doubly adaptive biased coin design with minimal variance strategy and
             maximal power strategy targeting 'Neyman' allocation and 'RSIHR' allocation, Bayesian response-adaptive randomization with 
             a control group using 'Thall' \& 'Wathen' method and the forward-looking 'Gittins' index rule.
